      "testConditions": {
        "en": "Weigh accurately not less than 20 Norgestrel and with 20 mL of the standard solution under the above operat-ing conditions, the relative standard deviation of the ratios of the peak area of ethinylestradiol and norgestrel to that of the internal standard are not more than 1.0z, respectively."
      }
    }
  ],
